      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs from two independent production lots tested across two laboratories. Dimensional inspection of each article via CMM prior to testing. All constructs within ±0.03 mm of nominal screw diameter. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison per ASME V&V 40 Table 3."
