      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 standard configuration (10° offset, 35 mm inter-body distance) at a single crosshead displacement rate (5 mm/min). Only one test condition evaluated. Achieved level 2 is below required level 3; this is a documented gap accepted by the submission team given the prescriptive nature of the F1717 standard and the corroborating multi-lab data."
