      "rationale": "All FEA boundary conditions (displacement rate, fixture geometry, block dimensions) set prior to experimental unblinding. Material parameters fixed from pre-test coupon data. No parameter tuning performed after experimental data were received. Equivalency confirmed by side-by-side comparison of model input deck against test protocol."
