      "acceptanceCriteria": "E/uval < 1.96 for all primary QoIs; percent difference < 10% for mean stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement.",
      "rationale": "Validation metric E/uval = (|y_exp_mean − y_sim|) / u_val computed for three QoIs: stiffness (E/uval = 0.84), yield force (E/uval = 1.12), force at 40 mm (E/uval = 0.67). All below 1.96 threshold. Mean percent differences: stiffness 3.2%, yield force 5.8%, force at 40 mm 4.1% — all within 10% bound. Achieved level 4 reflects quantitative probabilistic comparison with uncertainty propagation."
